Usage: ON [#|+|-|^|&|@]SEND_CTCP [-|^]<parameters> [action]
  This is activated whenever you send a CTCP to someone.
  The parameters for the action are as follows:
    $0    Type of the requeste (PRIVMSG)
    $1    The recipient
    $2    The CTCP request
    $3-   The parameters
